data.description:
Welcome to the PERFECT home for your family! One block away and a quick walk from Parkland Elementary School in Yukon’s coveted school district! This home backs up to Yukon's biggest and BEST public park system with walking trails right in from right down the street! This park is well known for its playgrounds, fishing lakes, walking trails, and Community Center with a pool as well as Yukon’s famous annual Christmas lights! This is the best family-friendly, established neighborhood around!


This beautiful home has been well loved. Home has fresh paint throughout,  beautiful wood floors, and wood burning fireplace! Spacious master has TWO closets as well as its own full bathroom! There is a big front porch to enjoy your morning coffee and a spacious backyard perfect for cookouts, not to mention the bonus space you can make into your office or formal dining space!!! Thrown in the ready-to-use alarm system/cameras and this house is ready to move in!


Best part of all about this home?!? It makes money FOR you! How? This house is 100% Electric (no gas heating) and 100% SOLAR!!!!! NO SURPRISE HEATING BILLS DURING WINTER STORMS!!!!!!!! With only your monthly connection fee with OG&E, not only is all your power taken care of, OG&E actually pays YOU for the electricity you don’t use!
Hurry, this home won’t last long!!!

*Special Incentive for VA qualified buyers!!!!
*Purchase price SIGNIFICANTLY negotiable with the assumption of current solar loan
